Now, we will build the client's system that receives and prorcesses market data updates from the trading exchange. 
Then also have to deal with creating and reading UDP sockets, dealing with packet losses. 
then the design of the order book on the client side to track the order book maintained at the trading exchange. 
Next, implement the components needed to establish and maintain TCP connection to the trading exchange. 
Last implement functionality to send orders to the exchange from the strategies and receive and process order responses. 


